    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing for a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring superb corner-exit rotation. The chassis remains remarkably composed, benefiting from reinforced subframe mounting points and a crisp MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension setup. While showing light patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical tolerances and drivetrain synchronization are exemplary.",
